    },
    {
      question: "Is the MOJ stamp accepted in Sharjah?",
      answer: "Yes. MOJ certification is federal and accepted across all Emirates. Our translations are accepted by Sharjah courts, government authorities, and all institutions in the emirate."
    },
    {
      question: "Do I need to come to Dubai?",
      answer: "No. Our complete workflow happens via WhatsApp. Send documents from Sharjah, receive translations delivered to your Sharjah address. No travel required."
    },
    {
      question: "Can you translate documents for Sharjah free zones?",
      answer: "Yes. Sharjah has several free zones including SAIF Zone, Sharjah Media City, and Sharjah Publishing City. We translate free zone documentation for banking, licensing, and other purposes."
    },
    {
      question: "Do you deliver to all Sharjah areas?",
      answer: "Yes. We deliver to all Sharjah locations including Al Nahda, Al Khan, Al Majaz, Al Qasimia, Industrial Areas, and surrounding communities. Delivery times are consistent across the emirate."
    }
  ],
  serviceType: "Legal Translation"
};
---

<ServiceLayout {...pageData}>
  
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Serving Sharjah from Dubai</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <p>Live in Sharjah? No need to travel to Dubai. We serve Sharjah with next-day delivery standard. Same-day available when urgent.</p>
        
        <div class="info-highlight">
          <h4><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> MOJ Certification is Federal</h4>
          <p>Our Dubai-certified translations are valid in Sharjah. All UAE courts and authorities accept them. No emirate distinction.</p>
        </div>
        
        <h3>How It Works for Sharjah</h3>
        <div class="workflow-steps">
          <div class="workflow-step">
            <span class="step-num">1</span>
            <div>
              <strong>WhatsApp your documents</strong>
              <p>From your Sharjah home or office</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="workflow-step">
            <span class="step-num">2</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Get instant quote</strong>
              <p>Response within minutes</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="workflow-step">
            <span class="step-num">3</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Receive delivery</strong>
              <p>Digital PDF immediately. Physical next-day.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p>Work in <a href="/locations/dubai/">Dubai</a> but live in Sharjah? Handle your translation needs without extra trips.</p>
        
        <h3>Sharjah's Character</h3>
        <p>Sharjah is the UAE's cultural capital. It hosts major universities and publishing industries. We understand these local contexts and common document needs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Common Translation Needs in Sharjah</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <div class="needs-grid">
          <div class="need-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Family Documents</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/personal/vital-records/birth/">Birth certificates</a> for school and visas</li>
              <li><a href="/personal/vital-records/marriage/">Marriage certificates</a> for sponsorship</li>
              <li><a href="/personal/vital-records/divorce/">Divorce decrees</a> for personal status</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Processing <a href="/services/golden-visa-translation/">Golden Visa</a>? We coordinate translation and <a href="/services/attestation/">attestation</a> together.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="need-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Educational Documents</h3>
            <p>Sharjah hosts major universities:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>University of Sharjah</li>
              <li>American University of Sharjah</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Need <a href="/personal/academic/degree/">degrees</a> and transcripts translated? We handle academic terminology correctly.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="need-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i> Employment Documents</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/legal/contracts/">Employment contracts</a></li>
              <li><a href="/personal/immigration/bank/">Salary certificates</a></li>
              <li>NOC letters</li>
            </ul>
            <p>MOHRE accepts our translations for all employment matters.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="need-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-building"></i> Business Documents</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/legal/corporate/moa/">MOA</a> and trade licenses</li>
              <li><a href="/legal/corporate/poa/">Powers of Attorney</a></li>
              <li><a href="/legal/corporate/resolution/">Board resolutions</a></li>
            </ul>
            <p>For banks, authorities, and cross-border dealings.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Sharjah Courts and Legal Matters</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <h3>Court Document Translation</h3>
        <p>Sharjah courts accept MOJ-certified translations for all <a href="/legal/litigation/">legal proceedings</a>. Whether you are filing a civil case, responding to a claim, or submitting evidence, translated documents with proper certification are accepted.</p>

        <p><a href="/services/legal-translation/">Legal translation</a> for Sharjah court matters follows the same standards as <a href="/locations/dubai/">Dubai</a> court work. Accuracy, proper legal terminology, and appropriate formatting all contribute to documents that support your legal position effectively. For <a href="/legal/litigation/verdict/">court verdicts</a> and <a href="/legal/litigation/arbitration/">arbitration awards</a>, we ensure precise legal terminology.</p>

        <h3>Personal Status Matters</h3>
        <p><a href="/personal/vital-records/divorce/">Divorce</a>, custody, inheritance, and other personal status matters often involve documents from outside the UAE. Foreign <a href="/personal/vital-records/marriage/">marriage certificates</a>, court orders, and official documents need certified translation for Sharjah court proceedings. We handle these sensitive matters with discretion. For inheritance cases, <a href="/legal/wills/">will translation</a> may be required.</p>

        <h3>Commercial Disputes</h3>
        <p>Business disputes before Sharjah courts may involve <a href="/legal/contracts/">contracts</a>, correspondence, and <a href="/specialized/financial/">financial documents</a> in languages other than Arabic. We translate commercial documentation for <a href="/legal/litigation/">litigation support</a>, meeting court requirements for evidentiary submissions.</p>

        <h3>Property and Tenancy</h3>
        <p>Sharjah has its own property registration system and tenancy dispute resolution. Documents for <a href="/industries/real-estate/">property transactions</a> or <a href="/legal/contracts/lease/">rental disputes</a> may need translation when parties or documentation involve non-Arabic elements. We also handle <a href="/legal/contracts/spa/">SPA translation</a> for property purchases.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Sharjah Free Zones</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <h3>SAIF Zone</h3>
        <p>Sharjah Airport International Free Zone hosts logistics, trading, and light industrial companies. SAIF Zone documentation—trade licenses, establishment cards, regulatory correspondence—may need translation for banking or mainland dealings.</p>
        
        <h3>Sharjah Media City (Shams)</h3>
        <p>Shams caters to media, creative, and freelance businesses. Companies registered in Shams may need translated documentation for bank accounts, visa processing, or contracts with mainland clients.</p>
        
        <h3>Sharjah Publishing City</h3>
        <p>This specialized free zone serves publishers, authors, and content creators. Translation needs may include contracts, rights agreements, and business documentation. Publishing-related translation aligns with Sharjah's role as UNESCO World Book Capital 2019.</p>
        
        <h3>Hamriyah Free Zone</h3>
        <p>Industrial and manufacturing focus in Hamriyah creates translation needs around contracts, regulatory documentation, and international trade paperwork. We handle industrial and commercial terminology appropriately.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Delivery Throughout Sharjah</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <h3>Central Sharjah</h3>
        <p>Al Nahda, Al Khan, Al Majaz, and downtown Sharjah areas receive next-day courier delivery as standard. Same-day delivery available for Express and VIP Concierge service.</p>
        
        <h3>Al Qasimia and Al Taawun</h3>
        <p>These busy commercial and residential areas are well-served by courier networks. Standard next-day delivery applies.</p>
        
        <h3>Industrial Areas</h3>
        <p>Sharjah's industrial zones—Industrial Area 1 through 18, Sajaa, and others—receive the same delivery service as residential areas. Documents can be delivered to business premises.</p>
        
        <h3>University City and Muwaileh</h3>
        <p>The educational district and surrounding residential areas have growing populations. Delivery service covers these areas with standard timing.</p>
        
        <h3>Other Sharjah Communities</h3>
        <p>All Sharjah locations are covered including Al Gharb, Al Juraina, Al Yarmook, and outlying areas. Delivery timing may vary slightly for remote locations but we confirm when you order.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Service Levels</h2>
      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>Standard</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">From AED 150</div>
          <p class="pricing-time">24-hour + next-day delivery</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>MOJ-certified translation</li>
            <li>Digital PDF immediately</li>
            <li>Next-day Sharjah courier</li>
            <li>WhatsApp updates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card pricing-card--featured">
          <h3>Express</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">From AED 300</div>
          <p class="pricing-time">6-hour + same-day courier</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Everything in Standard</li>
            <li>Priority processing</li>
            <li>Same-day Sharjah delivery</li>
            <li>Court deadline support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>VIP Concierge</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">From AED 500</div>
          <p class="pricing-time">1-hour draft + urgent courier</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Everything in Express</li>
            <li>Immediate assignment</li>
            <li>Draft within 60 minutes</li>
            <li>Urgent courier dispatch</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Getting Started</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <p>Send your documents via WhatsApp from anywhere in Sharjah. Personal documents, business papers, court filings—whatever needs translation. We will confirm requirements, timeline, and cost within minutes.</p>
        
        <p>If you are unsure what documents need translation for your specific purpose—visa application, court case, business registration—describe your situation and we will advise on the complete requirements.</p>
        
        <p>Digital copies arrive as soon as translation is complete. Physical copies with MOJ certification ship the same day, arriving next day to Sharjah addresses. For urgent matters, same-day courier gets documents to you faster.</p>
        
        <p>No Dubai travel required. Everything happens remotely, with certified translations delivered directly to your Sharjah address.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <InlineCallout 
        type="tip" 
        title="Common Sharjah Services"
        link="/services/attestation/"
        linkText="View attestation services"
      >
        Many Sharjah residents need attestation along with translation for documents from their home countries.
      </InlineCallout>

      <RelatedServices
        pageKey="sharjah"
        title="Common Document Needs"
        showFamily={true}
        showPrerequisites={true}
        showNextSteps={true}
        showCrossSilo={true}
        maxItems={8}
      />

      <CrossSiloLinks maxLinks={6} />
    </div>
  </section>

</ServiceLayout>

<style>
  .content-prose {
    max-width: 800px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  
  .content-prose h3 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }
  
  .content-prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }
  
  .content-prose a {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  .content-prose a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* Info Highlight */
  .info-highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e6f7ff 0%, #d6f0ff 100%);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-color);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0 0.75rem 0.75rem 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .info-highlight h4 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-size: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .info-highlight h4 i {
    color: var(--accent-color);
  }

  .info-highlight p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* Workflow Steps */
  .workflow-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

